description:
EXCLUSIVE OFFERS IN YOUR NEARBY STORES

Try great products at reduced prices. Simply buy, take a picture of your receipt, and get your cash back!

All offers are exclusive to Shopmium users and cannot be found elsewhere.

***

- Free registration - nothing to pay - ever!
- Discounts on all kinds of products: gourmet products, beverages, grocery, cosmetics, etc.
- New offers are introduced each week.
- No store constraints. You can redeem your offers at any store the product is sold.
- Very easy cash back process: rebates are processed within the app in just 2 clicks!
- Get your cash back directly to your PayPal or bank account.


Shopmium users have already taken advantage of many offers and free products, from companies like: Glade, Chobani, Tropicana, L'Oreal, Häagen-Dazs, Nestle, Evian, Vitamin Water… and many more!

SHOPMIUM is compatible with iPhone 3GS, 4, 4S, 5, 5C, 5S, 6 and 6+ and requires iOS 5.0 or later.
